					The EtiquetAR web application enables creating, collecting, printing and sharing personalized interactive QR. Users can associate one or more multimedia web resources to each of the QR tags. Once created, the Tags can be shared and updated by any other user of the community and grouped into collections for creating structured information paths. The QR codes can be tagged by the users to customize and glocalize objects of the urban spaces or of the cultural institutions.
